structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: Annual report -- Compliance with KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090.

text.section: The board shall annually file a written report concerning its operations with the county judge/executive.
The board shall comply with the provisions of KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090.

law.history: Amended 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 40, sec. 50, effective March 21, 2013. -- Created 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 21.
